Convert the two-level unitary matrices to quantum circuit elements consists \
of controlled-unitary and CNOT gates.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->111251633,ExpressionUUID->"e9f6ee9d-dd03-4984-8294-e244e9905ff1"],

